{"tid":241512,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺澳門人係講廣東話族最低質？","createTime":"2017-05-13T08:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T15:35:26.000Z","uid":15818,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef7f40eaaea31f5c6d24c8fca1aa56daccaa5d27","tid":241512,"uid":15818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"香港唔駛講 思想正想 有自己既觀點立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然都有藍c 同mk仔 但比較上進 因為被迫出黎<br />\n唔係點買樓 買波鞋去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬拉唐人 檳城一帶 睇tvb大都識廣東話<br />\n語言好 勤力肯做 做馬拉二等公民慣所以都較上進<br />\n想走出辣雞哥既統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大多祖藉潮州福建<br />\n<br />\n廣東人 唯一係中國有本土意識 較團結 但因中共係北佬掌權多 所以都受壓唔少 仲有推普機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佛山廣洲一帶基本都係唔少香港人故鄉<br />\n所以不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n移民加美英 97前走 最純正既有技術港人<br />\n基本上加拿大燒味炒飯屌打香港9成餐廳因為都係有技術先移到民賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大中華意識都有少少 但都係較為有錢有技術<br />\n平時睇tvb海外台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靚女多唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都會博殺下 唔會鳩流流咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n澳門人 無公開試 成個澳門都係由雞場賭場撐<br />\n基本上成街都街童<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無公開試就唔會想入大學或上進 打荷/荷包咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想讀就去台灣讀 讀下二三流大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全無本土意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n派幾千蚊就覺得屌打香港人 覺得港仔好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但出去外國會話自己係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上相處過下既澳門人都好似少條筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0084bee6baa9c9d1fbce96f16da52f0e1c28a74d","tid":241512,"uid":41205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"你咪咁講，澳門妹又白又滑又嗲d雞比得上台妹"},{"pid":"1a45089c9777d56d923e76a9c98b7b058e95140c","tid":241512,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"睇完篇文🇫🇷原來人無見識係一件好可悲既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0894734abe1d6ae2937d62c800c27f65bb2c61d","tid":241512,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"Ching sick ball"},{"pid":"159d04fffa3c77593177eff54426d67fe0a8abc7","tid":241512,"uid":88634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪咁講，澳門妹又白又滑又嗲d雞比得上台妹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得閒過海玩返轉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae26ca69adb4a68ab39cee3a3e7e98ad816f4936","tid":241512,"uid":12498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b39b89ff65138d7741d2b18f2691c74fd62374","tid":241512,"uid":59312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"打一句野彈一個腦魔出黎<br />\n睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"5f174fc586848682be8a8079d9a321d8b60c9434","tid":241512,"uid":15243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完篇文🇫🇷原來人無見識係一件好可悲既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 樓主邊忽有講錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3facae1a6f79a57b6b313f9be53357f0a181717","tid":241512,"uid":75533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完篇文🇫🇷原來人無見識係一件好可悲既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 樓主邊忽有講錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能佢講緊自己呢挺澳門賤種狗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e829420898b3fd1c1b3c1ba6a518349a73d29b6a","tid":241512,"uid":54278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"澳門狗係咁"},{"pid":"2b0d59e2fc7812af8b5098398336cf7511b0cd99","tid":241512,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"未見識過世界既人係咁既水平<br />\n<br />\n馬拉妹好多都係港女收兵狗<br />\n廣東話係好北姑少少（除非住左響到好耐）<br />\n同埋馬拉唔同地方唔同人種 d廣東話level又係唔一樣<br />\n但點都有陣大陸味<br />\n澳門你可以串佢文化唔高 但廣東話一定係除左香港之外最好 用既又係繁體字"},{"pid":"93c09b8858c6b950b7afa151d61e4fdcead903d4","tid":241512,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:25:14.000Z","msg":"廣東十幾個城市, 樓主直接用「廣東」就包含哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8617788d4d9d143d20fcb0663cafa3f52f487c","tid":241512,"uid":56872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"澳門人種無知真係好可悲"},{"pid":"38c737e750831002aa97fd09c42084f6a5244125","tid":241512,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未見識過世界既人係咁既水平<br />\n<br />\n馬拉妹好多都係港女收兵狗<br />\n廣東話係好北姑少少（除非住左響到好耐）<br />\n同埋馬拉唔同地方唔同人種 d廣東話level又係唔一樣<br />\n但點都有陣大陸味<br />\n澳門你可以串佢文化唔高 但廣東話一定係除左香港之外最好 用既又係繁體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廣州 有機會 高質過澳門<br />\n<br />\n但其他廣東城市 真係不值一提, 大部份都係生番地區 (多北佬都係其中一個原因, 但本地人唔見得好)"}]}